io.rouz.task.dsl

Interface TaskBuilder


  • public interface TaskBuilder
    Types for the fluent task setup API The entry point for this api is Task.named(String, Object...). Note, the inner types should never have to explicitly be mentioned or imported. The API is supposed to be used through fluent calls that eventually lead to a Task instance.
